entry.title: broadinstitute/smartseq2-single-nucleus-multisample
entry.summary: The Smart-seq2 Single Nucleus Multi-Sample (Multi-snSS2) pipeline was developed in collaboration with the BRAIN Initiative Cell Census Network (BICCN) to process single-nucleus RNAseq (snRNAseq) data generated by Smart-seq2 assays.
